page.title: 14ISABEL'S DAY
page.content: I usually get up at half past seven and then I get changed and go down to breakfast which takes about 45 minutes and then I go and feed my rabbits. Next I am off to clean my teeth and then to go to school at about 8.45. At 12.OO we go for lunch to the canteen across the road. After lunch when we come back we will stay on for another 3 and a half hours at school and then we go home. When I get home I have to go and feed my rabbits and then get changed and mess around and have some tea then at about half past seven we have supper. In the time between I usually watch the television and watch through and after supper and I then go to bed at about half past 9.OO to 1O.OO.
